e Stylus Phantasticus and Free Keyboard Music of the North German Baroque|year=2005|publisher=Ashgate Publishing|isbn=9780754634164}}\n*{{citation|title=Remains of Myles Coverdale|chapter=Ghostly Psalms and Spiritual Songs|volume=14|series=Parker Society|first=Miles|last=Coverdale|authorlink=Miles Coverdale|editor-first=George|editor-last= Pearson|date=1846|publisher=[[Cambridge University Press]]|chapter-url=https://archive.org/stream/parkersociety16coveuoft#page/n597/mode/2up|pages=571\u2013572}}\n*{{citation|chapter=Inventing the Bach chorale|title=Engaging Bach: The Keyboard Legacy from Marpurg to Mendelssohn|first=Matthew|last= Dirst|series=Musical Performance and Reception|publisher=[[Cambridge University Press]]|year=2012|isbn=978-0521651608|pages=34\u201354}}\n*{{citation|title=The Routledge Research Companion to Johann Sebastian Bach|editor-first=Robin A. |editor-last=Leaver|publisher=Taylor & Francis| year=2017|isbn=9781409417903|chapter=Early Posthumous Published Editions|first=Matthew|last=Dirst|pages=464\u2013474}}\n*{{citation|first=Alfred|last= D\u00fcrr|authorlink=Alfred D\u00fcrr|title=Zur Chronologie der Leipziger Vokalwerke J. S. Bachs |language=de|journal=[[Bach-Jahrbuch]]| volume=44|year=1957|pages=5\u2013162}}\n*{{citation|first=Alfred|last= D\u00fcrr|authorlink=Alfred D\u00fcrr|title= Zur Chronologie der Leipziger Vokalwerke J. S. Bachs. Zweite Auflage: Mit Anmerkungen und Nachtr\u00e4gen versehener Nachdruck aus Bach-Jahrbuch |language=de|publisher=[[B\u00e4renreiter]]|year=1976}}\n*{{NDB|3|465|466|Dachstein, Wolfgang|Forna\u00e7on, Siegfried|119650967}}\n*{{citation|title=Johann Sebastian Bach: Life and Work|first=Martin|last=Geck|translator=John Hargraves|publisher=[[Houghton Mifflin Harcourt]]|year=2006|isbn=0151006482|url-access=registration|url=https://archive.org/details/johannsebastianb00geck}}\n*{{citation |last = Greschat |first =Martin|title =Martin Bucer: A Reformer and His Times|publisher = Westminster John Knox Press|year =2004|i